78
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:18,600
Xi'er!

79
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:20,120
Xi'er!

80
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:22,040
Are you alright?

81
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,360
So it's you.

82
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,680
Don't even think about stopping this formation!

83
00:05:31,870 --> 00:05:33,360
Let the Nine-Headed Kui'ao

84
