109
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,870
He must have been bewitched by some evil being

110
00:08:01,030 --> 00:08:02,040
and gained some kind of power.

111
00:08:02,630 --> 00:08:04,040
If he really was bewitched by an evil being,

112
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,800
then everything he's done

113
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,360
is to create resentment

114
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,480
and nourish that evil being.

115
00:08:10,860 --> 00:08:11,980
This formation is expanding.

116
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,680
I don't know how long

117
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,480
this barrier can hold.

118
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:16,430
I wonder

119
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:17,870
if there's some hidden secret here.

120
00:08:18,190 --> 00:08:19,000
Let's split up

121
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,320
and look for a way to escape.

122
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,840
Heaven is truly on my side!

123
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,720
I never expected

124
00:08:37,740 --> 00:08:39,190
such a powerful evil being to be here now.

125
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:41,549
This is the perfect opportunity

126
00:08:41,750 --> 00:08:43,150
to get rid of these nuisances.

127
00:08:50,510 --> 00:08:51,750
This spell is...

128
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,930
Back then, they used this formation

129
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:54,670
against me.

130
00:08:55,630 --> 00:08:57,670
Now, I'll return the favor

131
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,550
in kind.

132
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:01,910
Won't that be interesting?

133
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:34,880
It looks like

134
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:36,120
no one has lived here for a long time.

135
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:38,720
Being able to set up such a powerful barrier,

136
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:39,720
the owner

137
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,720
must not be an ordinary person.

138
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:42,410
But we can't

139
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,550
just keep hiding here forever.

140
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,120
Otherwise, we'll be trapped to death sooner or later.

141
00:09:46,470 --> 00:09:46,900
Oh, right.

142
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,220
That Nine-Headed Kui'ao can call people's names,

143
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,870
and only when you respond does it bewitch you.

144
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,720
So let's each choose a codename

145
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,030
and only call each other by that.

146
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:56,390
If you hear someone calling your real name,

147
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:57,520
don't answer

148
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:58,080
and don't look.

149
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,510
That way, we won't fall into its trap.

150
00:10:00,270 --> 00:10:01,030
Mr. Yu,

151
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:02,870
