152
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:03,510
Master,

153
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,550
you'll be "Pumpkin."

154
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:05,750
What a coincidence.

155
00:10:06,350 --> 00:10:07,120
Qingge's

156
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:08,200
favorite dish

157
00:10:08,220 --> 00:10:09,120
used to be taro,

158
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:10,630
