159
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:11,910
was pumpkin.

160
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,150
Change it.

161
00:10:14,510 --> 00:10:15,000
Also,

162
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,940
he's not allowed to be called "Taro."

163
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:21,550
It's just a temporary codename.

164
00:10:23,510 --> 00:10:24,240
Alright.

165
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:26,120
Well, Master, you can be...

166
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:26,720
"Ice Lotus."

167
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:28,240
Mr. Yu,

168
00:10:28,630 --> 00:10:29,320
you can be "Lingxi."

169
00:10:30,790 --> 00:10:31,360
Change it again.

170
00:10:33,910 --> 00:10:35,050
Then you can be Su the First,

171
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,790
and you can be Su the Second.

172
00:10:36,290 --> 00:10:37,250
Why is he the first

173
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,120
and I the second?

174
00:10:39,390 --> 00:10:39,870
No.

175
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:42,880
A Crown Prince

176
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,670
and an immortal master.

177
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,910
Two prominent figures

178
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,350
