179
00:10:54,910 --> 00:10:55,440
Mr. Yu,

180
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:57,270
let me help you with your wound.

181
00:11:01,390 --> 00:11:01,960
Yu,

182
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:03,510
bear the pain.

183
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,240
Ranran,

184
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,390
you resemble an old friend of mine.

185
00:11:21,510 --> 00:11:22,270
Crown Prince,

186
00:11:22,870 --> 00:11:24,510
