187
00:11:26,810 --> 00:11:27,940
Why don't you check on Xi'er and the others?

188
00:11:28,910 --> 00:11:30,670
The matter between Master Mu and Mr. Yu

189
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,510
has already been settled.

190
00:11:32,390 --> 00:11:33,240
Master still can't

191
00:11:33,270 --> 00:11:34,790
let go of Master Mu

192
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:37,280
and keeps clashing with Mr. Yu.

193
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:45,510
Do your job as the Crown Prince well

194
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:47,150
and stay away from my disciples.

195
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,030
Is it staying away from your disciples

196
00:11:49,630 --> 00:11:51,390
or just from Ranran?

197
00:11:52,150 --> 00:11:52,870
You clearly

198
00:11:52,870 --> 00:11:53,960
don't care about anything,

199
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:56,390
but you're so concerned about Ranran.

200
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:58,150
Could it be that Ranran's identity

201
00:11:59,200 --> 00:11:59,960
is very special?

202
00:12:00,870 --> 00:12:02,320
Why should I explain to you

203
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:04,120
