205
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:07,480
You,

206
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:08,660
a treacherous person,

207
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:11,870
only hurts those who treat you well.

208
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:13,430
How could Ranran,

209
00:12:13,460 --> 00:12:14,460
such a pure and kind girl,

210
00:12:14,650 --> 00:12:16,220
stay by your side?

211
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:17,840
She can only have

212
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:19,050
the life she wants

213
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,360
if she comes with me.

214
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,440
Don't you dare come near her again.

215
00:12:42,050 --> 00:12:42,810
Could it really be that

216
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:44,430
the drop of Spirit Spring in my heart hasn't been fully removed,

217
00:12:45,270 --> 00:12:46,510
so now, the closer I get to the Spirit Spring,

218
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,080
the stronger the reaction?

219
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:51,480
Master,

220
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:52,510
Ranran found a hidden compartment.

221
00:12:59,340 --> 00:13:00,070
There's a hidden compartment?

222
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,910
Ranran, how did you know about it?

223
00:13:03,550 --> 00:13:04,910
I don't know why,

224
00:13:04,940 --> 00:13:06,610
but I just couldn't resist tapping it.

225
00:13:07,890 --> 00:13:09,200
Immortal, please forgive us.

226
00:13:13,550 --> 00:13:14,120
This is...

227
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:25,000
It's her.

228
00:13:29,030 --> 00:13:30,320
Qingge doesn't like using sound transmission talismans,

229
00:13:31,090 --> 00:13:32,330
so she made wooden figurines specifically

230
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,000
to send messages for her.

231
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:34,840
