233
00:13:40,670 --> 00:13:41,240
Could it be...

234
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:43,450
that this is really the place

235
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,890
where Qingge once lived?

236
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:52,760
There's a booklet here.

237
00:13:56,550 --> 00:13:58,240
It does look like

238
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,600
Master Mu's handwriting.

239
00:14:00,670 --> 00:14:01,750
Sister Wu?

240
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:05,670
It really is hers.

241
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:11,940
[Tranquility Pavilion]

242
00:14:12,100 --> 00:14:13,690
This seems to be

243
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:14,960
some of Master Mu's notes.

244
00:14:15,490 --> 00:14:16,010
Could there be

245
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:17,670
information about the Nine-Headed Kui'ao?

246
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,270
In March of the Year of Yuangui,

247
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,320
I received help from Uncle Ye Xin.

248
00:14:26,670 --> 00:14:28,320
So it seems that Master Mu learned

249
00:14:28,510 --> 00:14:29,080
all of her abilities

250
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,030
from this person named Ye Xin.

251
00:14:31,420 --> 00:14:32,240
He must be someone

252
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,000
who's incredibly capable.

253
00:14:35,670 --> 00:14:37,440
This must be Uncle Ye Xin's portrait.

254
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:40,080
Master.

255
00:14:43,910 --> 00:14:44,960
It's strange though—

256
00:14:45,630 --> 00:14:46,170
where...

257
00:14:46,270 --> 00:14:47,840
