258
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:50,360
How come he never appeared

259
00:14:50,670 --> 00:14:51,750
during major events

260
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:52,600
like Master Mu's death

261
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,630
and resurrection?

262
00:14:55,900 --> 00:14:56,870
Since he's a master,

263
00:14:56,910 --> 00:14:58,670
could it be that he completed his cultivation and ascended

264
00:14:58,750 --> 00:14:59,720
when he was traveling the world?

265
00:15:02,550 --> 00:15:03,240
This person...

266
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:05,030
