269
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,080
In May of the Year of Tianyi,

270
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,440
unexpectedly,

271
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:26,090
I met the young master from years ago

272
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:28,120
