276
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:40,670
who have faced hardships together.

277
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:42,320
From now on, just call me by my name.

278
00:15:43,150 --> 00:15:43,750
Alright.

279
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:45,140
