280
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:46,550
From now on, I'll call you Yu.

281
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:51,810
Turns out, Master Mu

282
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:53,200
and the Crown Prince had known each other

283
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:54,300
even before meeting Master.

284
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:02,600
Back then, I just

285
00:16:02,630 --> 00:16:03,910
gave Qingge some pastry.

286
00:16:04,910 --> 00:16:06,720
Qingge said she would repay this kindness,

287
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:08,870
but I thought she was only saying it casually.

288
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:10,320
I never expected her

289
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,840
to work so hard in cultivation

290
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:14,550
just to fulfill her promise.

